import Axios from 'axios'; import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react' const Contact_list = () => { const [contactData , setContactData] = useState([]); useEffect(()=>{ Axios.get('https://reqres.in/api/users?_limit=4') .then(res=>{ console.log(res.data) setContactData(res.data.data) }) },[]) return (
{ contactData.map((row)=>(

{row.first_name}

{row.last_name}

{row.email}

4:40 PM

)) }
) } export default Contact_list
